      "hook": "That spinach you bought Monday? Gone by Thursday.",
      "body_copy": "You stand there Tuesday night, staring into the fridge. The spinach you were so sure you'd use. The bell peppers that seemed like such a good idea. The yogurt that expires tomorrow.\n\nIt's not about willpower. It's not about being organized enough.\n\nIt's that the gap between buying food and actually using it has never been properly connected. You plan, you shop, then... somehow it all falls apart in your actual kitchen.\n\nYou're not failing. The system is.",
