      "hook": "You tracked. You planned. You still threw out the spinach.",
      "body_copy": "The meal planning apps told you to prep on Sunday. The grocery lists were perfect. You had every ingredient mapped out.\n\nBut Tuesday came and nobody wanted the planned dinner. Thursday the kids rejected lunch. Weekend hit and half your fresh groceries were wilting.\n\nThe problem isn't your planning skills. The system is disconnected from real family life.",
