      "hook": "Monday meal plan. Wednesday takeout. Friday what's in the fridge?",
      "body_copy": "Sound familiar? You start each week with good intentions. Plan healthy meals. Buy fresh ingredients. Then life happens.\n\nBy Wednesday, you're ordering pizza again. By Friday, you're staring at wilted lettuce wondering what went wrong.\n\nThe problem isn't your willpower. It's that meal planning and grocery shopping exist in separate worlds. No wonder nothing connects.",
