      "platform": "Instagram",
      "hook": "What if your fridge knew what was expiring before you opened it?",
      "body_copy": "I used to find wilted lettuce and forgotten yogurt every week. The guilt was real.\n\nThen I realized something: I wasn't the problem. My system was broken.\n\nLook at this screen. easyChef Pro tracks what you have and when it expires. Before you even open the fridge door, you know exactly what needs to be used first.\n\nNo more surprise discoveries. No more throwing money away. Just clear visibility into what you actually have.\n\nIt's like having X-ray vision for your kitchen. The app remembers so you don't have to.\n\nThis isn't about being more organized. It's about having a system that actually works with how busy life really is.\n\nThe waste stops. The guilt stops. The constant mental load of trying to remember everything? That stops too.\n\nSometimes the solution isn't trying harder. It's finding the right tool.",
