      "hook": "One scan closes the invisible leak. TRACK to COOK in one app.",
      "body_copy": "You know that moment when you open the fridge and somehow nothing connects to dinner?\n\nThe ingredients are there. The recipes exist somewhere. But the bridge between what you have and what you can make feels... missing.\n\nThat's the invisible leak.\n\neasyChef Pro closes it with one simple scan. Point your phone at any ingredient in your fridge, pantry, or cart. The app instantly knows what you have and shows you exactly what you can cook tonight.\n\nNo more staring into the void of your refrigerator. No more buying ingredients that sit unused. No more 6 PM panic about dinner.\n\nOne scan. Your ingredients become your possibilities.\n\nThe system was disconnected. Now it flows.\n\n30 minutes fridge to table, every single time.",
