      "id": "ec001-sp-104",
      "campaign_id": "EC-2026-001",
      "platform": "Instagram",
      "hook": "The gap between apps is where $111 goes. This closes the gap.",
      "body_copy": "You know that feeling when you're standing in the grocery store, staring at your phone, juggling three different apps? One for recipes, one for your shopping list, another trying to figure out what's actually in your fridge right now.\n\nThat's where the money disappears. In the gaps.\n\nYou buy ingredients for the recipe app. Then grab extras because the shopping app reminded you. Then pick up backup options because nothing connects to what you actually have at home.\n\neasyChef Pro does something different. Everything lives in one place. Your meal plans see your real grocery inventory. Your shopping lists know what recipes you're making. Your fridge contents talk to your dinner plans.\n\nNo more buying cilantro three times because three apps don't talk to each other.\n\nNo more 6 PM panic when the recipe calls for something you're sure you bought but can't find.\n\nNo more throwing away food because nothing was planned around what you already had.\n\n30 minutes from fridge to table. Every time. Because when everything connects, cooking becomes simple again.\n\nThe problem was never you. The system was disconnected.",
      "cta": "Join thousands who stopped the waste spiral",
