      "hook": "PLAN builds five dinners from what you already own.",
      "body_copy": "Tuesday night. You open your fridge and see the usual suspects: leftover chicken, half a bag of spinach, some rice from Sunday.\n\nBefore, this would mean another frantic grocery run or ordering takeout again. But now? You tap PLAN in easyChef Pro.\n\nIt sees your chicken and suggests a creamy spinach skillet. Your rice becomes the base for a quick fried rice with those frozen peas you forgot about. That yogurt you bought? Perfect for marinating tomorrow's chicken.\n\nFive complete dinners appear. No shopping list. No panic. Just dinner solutions from what's already yours.\n\nYour kids don't know you're working magic with leftovers. They just know dinner tastes good and mom isn't stressed.\n\nThe best part? Saturday morning feels different now. Instead of dreading the week ahead, you're actually looking forward to trying that new way to use ground beef.\n\nThis is what happens when the system finally works with you instead of against you.",
