      "hook": "OPTIMIZE: six nutrition dimensions. No tracking required.",
      "body_copy": "Picture this: It's 4 PM and you're not panicking about dinner.\n\nYour kids ask what's for dinner and you actually know. Because easyChef Pro already mapped out meals that work for everyone — the picky eater gets something they'll actually eat, you get the nutrients you've been missing, and nobody's hangry.\n\nNo more standing in the grocery store wondering if you have enough protein this week. No more 'is this actually balanced?' anxiety. The system sees the whole picture — protein, fiber, vitamins, minerals, healthy fats, and variety — so you don't have to.\n\nYour daughter gets her energy back. Your partner stops the afternoon crashes. You stop feeling like you're failing at the most basic thing.\n\nBecause when the system works, everything flows. Meals happen. Bodies get what they need. And that mental load you've been carrying? It lifts.\n\neasyChef Pro handles the nutrition science. You handle the love.",
