      "campaign_id": "EC-2026-001",
      "platform": "Facebook",
      "hook": "30 minutes. Fridge to table. COOK turns your pantry into dinner.",
      "body_copy": "Picture this: It's 5:47 PM. Kids are asking what's for dinner. You open your fridge, and instead of that familiar panic, you feel... calm. Because easyChef Pro already knows what's in there. It sees the chicken thighs, the bag of rice, those wilting greens you forgot about. In seconds, it shows you exactly how to turn them into something your family will actually eat. No emergency grocery runs. No takeout guilt. Just dinner, handled.",
