      "hook": "30 minutes. Fridge to table. COOK turns your pantry into dinner.",
      "body_copy": "Picture this: It's 5:47 PM. Kids are asking what's for dinner. You open your fridge and instead of that familiar sinking feeling, you smile.\n\nBecause easyChef Pro already knows what's in there. It sees the leftover chicken, those bell peppers from Tuesday, that can of coconut milk you forgot about.\n\nYour phone lights up: \"Mediterranean Chicken Bowl - 22 minutes.\" The recipe uses exactly what you have. No emergency grocery runs. No takeout guilt.\n\nWhile dinner simmers, you're helping with homework instead of frantically googling \"what to make with chicken and peppers.\" The kitchen timer goes off. Everyone sits down together.\n\nThis is what happens when your meal planning actually works with your real life. When the system knows your pantry, your schedule, your family's preferences.\n\nNo more standing in your kitchen at dinner time wondering how other moms make it look so easy. Because now you have what they have - a system that actually connects the dots.\n\nEverything you need is already in your kitchen. You just needed something smart enough to see it.",
