      "body_copy": "Right now you're juggling toddler snacks and family dinners. Next year it's school lunches and after-school chaos. Then teen appetites and college prep meals.\n\neasyChef Pro grows with every stage. From finger foods to family feasts to teaching your kids to cook. One app, every chapter of motherhood.\n\nBuilt for where you are today and where you're headed tomorrow.",
