      "platform": "Instagram",
      "hook": "Join the founding family. The app that evolves with your life.",
      "body_copy": "You're in the thick of it now. Soccer practice, piano lessons, work deadlines, and somehow dinner still needs to happen. This is the season where everything moves fast and you're managing it all.\n\nBut here's what we know about you: you're not staying here forever. The kids will get older. Schedules will shift. Your family's needs will change.\n\neasyChef Pro was built for this exact journey. Right now, it handles the chaos of your current life — quick meals between activities, lunches that actually get eaten, dinners that bring everyone together even when time is short.\n\nBut as your family grows and changes, so does easyChef Pro. When the kids start cooking with you. When they leave for college and it's just the two of you again. When they come home with their own families.\n\nThis isn't just meal planning for today. It's meal planning that understands your whole story — where you are now and where you're headed next.\n\nYour family's food story is still being written. easyChef Pro grows with every chapter.",
