      "body_copy": "You're in the thick of toddler chaos now—snack demands, picky phases, mealtime negotiations. But school-age is coming. Different schedules, different appetites, different needs.\n\neasyChef Pro moves through each stage with you. From purees to packed lunches to family dinners that actually work. The meal planning that grows as your family grows.\n\nThis is motherhood in motion. Your kitchen confidence, evolving.",
