      "campaign_id": "EC-2026-001",
      "platform": "Instagram",
      "hook": "10,000 households. 69.5% less waste. $1,336 average savings.",
      "body_copy": "Sarah from Denver tracks every grocery dollar. Three kids, two jobs, one overwhelmed kitchen. Sound familiar?\n\nBefore easyChef Pro: \"I'd buy ingredients with good intentions, then watch half of them expire. The guilt was crushing.\"\n\nAfter easyChef Pro: \"My grocery bill dropped $111 per month. But honestly? The relief of not throwing away food anymore — that's priceless.\"\n\nThe data backs what Sarah experienced. Validated across 10,000 household profiles, families using easyChef Pro reduce food waste by 69.5% on average. Real families. Real kitchens. Real savings.\n\nBuilt by first responders who understood that meal planning isn't about perfect recipes — it's about systems that work when life gets messy. 9 patent-pending technologies working behind the scenes so you don't have to.\n\nThe problem was never that you couldn't plan meals. The system was disconnected from how real families actually eat.\n\neasyChef Pro closes those gaps.",
      "cta": "Join thousands saving money and reducing waste",
      "hashtags": "#easychefpro #foodtech #kitchenapp #firstresponders #familyfood #innovation #instafood #momstagram #mealprepping #foodblogger #kitchenlife",
