    {
      "id": "ec001-sp-147",
      "campaign_id": "EC-2026-001",
      "platform": "Pinterest",
      "hook": "10,000 households. 69.5% less waste. $1,336 average savings.",
      "body_copy": "Real families. Real results. Real food that doesn't end up in the trash.\n\nWhen the Hendersons started using easyChef Pro, they thought maybe they'd save a little money. Instead, they cut their grocery waste by over half and put an extra $1,336 back in their budget.\n\nIt's not about being perfect. It's about having a system that actually works with your life.\n\nValidated across 10,000 household profiles.",
