      "hook": "69.5% less food waste. Validated across 10,000 profiles.",
      "body_copy": "Sarah from Denver shared her grocery receipts with us. Before easyChef Pro: $847/month on groceries, throwing away wilted lettuce, expired yogurt, forgotten leftovers.\n\nAfter 3 months with easyChef Pro: $531/month. Same family of four. Same dietary preferences. Same busy schedule.\n\nThe difference? easyChef Pro's system tracks what you actually have, plans meals around expiration dates, and suggests portions based on your family's real eating patterns.\n\nNo more buying duplicate ingredients. No more mystery containers in the back of the fridge. No more guilt over wasted money.\n\nThis isn't about being a better meal planner. The old system was broken. You were doing everything right with incomplete information.\n\neasyChef Pro gives you the complete picture: what you have, what you need, when to use it. The result is less waste, lower bills, and the confidence that comes from a system that actually works.\n\nThat's how Sarah joined thousands of families who've cut their food waste by 69.5% — not through willpower, but through better information.",
