      "hook": "$1,336/year. 69.5% less waste. 30 min fridge to table. Real numbers.",
      "body_copy": "These aren't marketing promises. They're validated across 10,000 household profiles.\n\nReal families. Real kitchens. Real results.\n\nThe mom in Denver who stopped throwing away half her groceries. The working parent in Phoenix who finally gets dinner on the table before bedtime stories. The family in Atlanta who cut their food budget by over a thousand dollars.\n\nThey're not superhuman. They just stopped fighting a broken system.\n\nBefore easyChef Pro, meal planning meant guessing what you'd actually cook, buying ingredients that expired in the back of your fridge, and scrambling every night at 6 PM.\n\nThe system was disconnected. Your shopping list didn't talk to your schedule. Your pantry didn't talk to your recipes. Your family's preferences got lost in the chaos.\n\neasyChef Pro closes those gaps. Every ingredient connects to a specific meal. Every meal fits your actual timeline. Every recipe adapts to what you already have.\n\nThe result? 69.5% less food waste. $1,336 back in your pocket. 30 minutes from fridge to table, consistently.\n\nThousands of families proved it works. The data doesn't lie.",
