      "body_copy": "Every family that joins easyChef Pro becomes part of something bigger. A movement of parents who refuse to accept that feeding their family well should be this hard.\n\nWe're the first 5,000 families building kitchens that actually work. Where meal planning takes 10 minutes, not hours. Where grocery lists write themselves. Where your family eats better while you save $200+ every month.\n\nThis isn't about perfection. It's about belonging to a community that gets it. Parents who understand that the system was broken, not you.\n\neasyChef Pro connects everything that should have been connected from the start. Your meal plans sync to smart grocery lists. Your preferences learn and adapt. Your kitchen becomes the heart of your home again.\n\nFor the first 5,000 founding families: $7.99/month (60% off forever). Because the parents building the future of family meals deserve to save the most.\n\nYour spot is waiting. Your family's kitchen revolution starts today.",
