      "hook": "The founding price closes when 5,000 spots fill.",
      "body_copy": "Sarah saved $2,847 this year. Not because she changed who she is as a mom. Because she found a system that actually works.\n\nBefore easyChef Pro, she was spending $180+ weekly on groceries that half went bad. Ordering takeout when dinner planning felt impossible. Feeling like she was failing at something that should be simple.\n\nThe problem was never her. The system was disconnected.\n\neasyChef Pro closes the gaps:\n→ Smart meal plans that use what you already have\n→ Grocery lists that eliminate waste\n→ 15-minute meals when life gets crazy\n→ One system that actually talks to itself\n\nSarah's family now eats better for 60% less. Same busy life. Same three kids. Different system.\n\nWe're holding the founding price of $7.99/month (60% off forever) for the first 5,000 families who want to join us.\n\nNot because of urgency. Because we're building something different together. A community where the system works for real families, not against them.\n\nYou already know if this is for you. The door is open when you're ready.",
