      "hook": "July 1. The founding family gets first access. You in?",
      "body_copy": "Sarah used to spend $200+ weekly on groceries that half went bad. Sound familiar?\n\nThe problem was never her planning skills. The system was disconnected.\n\nShe'd meal plan Sunday, shop Tuesday, then life happened. Soccer practice moved. Work ran late. The beautiful plan crumbled.\n\neasyChef Pro closes those gaps. Your meal plans sync with your actual schedule. Grocery lists auto-adjust when plans change. Recipe portions scale instantly when friends join dinner.\n\nSarah now spends $120 weekly. Same family. Better meals. Zero waste.\n\nThe founding families who join July 1st get easyChef Pro for $7.99/month — that's 60% off forever. First 5,000 families only.\n\nNot because we're rushing you. Because you've been walking toward this solution already. Every Sunday you've planned. Every grocery trip you've optimized. Every dinner you've improvised.\n\nYou belong with families who refuse to let disconnected systems waste their time and money.\n\n60-day money-back guarantee. Because when the system finally works with you instead of against you, you'll know within the first week.",
